            "text": "<p><strong>Perfume boxes by scent family – a sensory journey through the worlds of scent. Each scent family is a story in itself – a world of sensations, depth and unique energy that reaches straight to the senses and soul. In the collection of Heaven boxes by scent family, you can discover and connect with a wide variety of worlds in perfumery – from Leather and Citrus boxes, through Floral and Woody, to Gourmand and Aromatic – all in carefully designed packages, which provide a luxurious and focused sensory experience. Each box includes 5 carefully selected fragrances, so that you can experiment, discover and connect with a wide variety of fragrant styles and energies. Each box is a journey of discovery – an experience that connects the senses to the soul, allows you to get to know the style and depth of each fragrant family, and gives a sense of presence, confidence and pleasure at every moment. Choose the scent family box that suits you, and let the boxes lead you on a deep, stimulating sensory journey. Inspiring and unforgettable, where each fragrant family tells its own story.</strong></p>",
